- cs.ME (Mechanical Engineering) is another possible category as the paper deals with the dynamics of bipedal locomotion and the 3D Linear Inverted Pendulum model. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is a possible category as the paper involves numerical simulations. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a less likely category as the paper does not explicitly discuss machine learning or AI techniques, but it may be relevant in the context of control and optimization.
